OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772118239
OL,3,CPrincipal vows pupils 'will not be
OL,4,Cpushed into mainstream education'
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FThe headteacher of the Promise School
OL,8,Fin Okehampton has insisted pupils will
OL,9,Fnot be forced into mainstream
OL,10,Feducation after a huge fire destroyed
OL,11,Fthe school building.
OL,13,FHeadteacher, Qunetin Gunderson,
OL,14,Fspeaking after seeing the devastation
OL,15,Ffor the first time, said: "I am
OL,16,Fconfident the children won't be pushed
OL,17,Fback into mainstream education.
OL,19,F"We will make sure the provision they
OL,20,Fneed remains in place."
OL,26,@wD@[OU{D@AOU|D@WO]
