CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772118239
OL,3,CPrincipal vows pupils 'will not be
OL,4,Cpushed into mainstream education'
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FResidents and families have been urged
OL,8,Fto stay away from the Promise School
OL,9,Fafter the fire, which started on
OL,10,FSunday 22 February.
OL,12,FIt means more than 80 pupils will not
OL,13,Fbe able to attend their lessons as
OL,14,Fnormal, following the half term break.
OL,16,FFirefighters worked through Sunday
OL,17,Fnight to tackle the flames and
OL,18,Fremained on the scene till yesterday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
