FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772118239
OL,3,CPrincipal vows pupils 'will not be
OL,4,Cpushed into mainstream education'
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FFirefighters worked through Sunday
OL,8,Fnight to tackle the flames and
OL,9,Fremained at the scene until the
OL,10,Ffollowing day. Devon and Somerset Fire
OL,11,Fand Rescue Service said 18 crews
OL,12,Fattended at the height of the fire,
OL,13,Fwith six fire appliances, two aerial
OL,14,Fladder platforms and two water
OL,15,Fcarriers used.
OL,17,FMr Gunderson said he was "incredibly
OL,18,Fgrateful" to Devon and Somerset Fire
OL,19,Fand Rescue Service for their swift
OL,20,Fresponse.
OL,26,@yD@ZOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772118239
OL,3,CPrincipal vows pupils 'will not be
OL,4,Cpushed into mainstream education'
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FDescribing the destruction, Mr
OL,8,FGunderson said: "It's shocking. We can
OL,9,Fsee it's a complete catastrophic loss,
OL,10,Fthe building has gone, but the school
OL,11,Fremains, and we will come back
OL,12,Fstronger."
OL,14,FHe said the response from the
OL,15,Fcommunity had been overwhelming.
OL,17,F"We have been overwhelmed by the
OL,18,Fresponse from the local community,
OL,19,Fparents and businesses, everyone has
OL,20,Frallied around us.
OL,26,@pD@QOUtD@JO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
