PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772118239
OL,3,CPrincipal vows pupils 'will not be
OL,4,Cpushed into mainstream education'
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,F"We are working to get learning back
OL,8,Fonline as soon as possible."
OL,10,FHard-copy work packs have been printed
OL,11,Fand hand-delivered to families, with
OL,12,Fonline learning resuming immediately
OL,13,Fas a short-term measure.
OL,15,F"This is not going to be normal for a
OL,16,Flittle while," he said.
OL,18,F"But we are doing everything we can to
OL,19,Fmake sure there is continuity."
OL,26,@pD@\O]wD@AOUxD@NO]zD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772118239
OL,3,CPrincipal vows pupils 'will not be
OL,4,Cpushed into mainstream education'
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FHe added that leaders had been
OL,8,Fexploring temporary accommodation
OL,9,Foptions and were confident face-to-
OL,10,Fface learning could resume as early as
OL,11,Fthe end of next week, with priority
OL,12,Fgiven to primary pupils and those
OL,13,Fpreparing for GCSEs.
OL,15,F"Of course the children are upset,
OL,16,Ftheir school is gone.
OL,18,F"So it's about reassurance. We will
OL,19,Fget learning back for them as soon as
OL,20,Fwe can."
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772118239
OL,3,CPrincipal vows pupils 'will not be
OL,4,Cpushed into mainstream education'
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FAlthough coursework and materials were
OL,8,Flost, he said they would be replaced
OL,9,Fand insurers were involved.
OL,11,F"There will be some distress caused by
OL,12,Fthat, and we will support our
OL,13,Fstudents. The things that have gone
OL,14,Fcan be replaced, we can order new
OL,15,Fbooks."
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
