FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1772118239
OL,3,CPrincipal vows pupils 'will not be
OL,4,Cpushed into mainstream education'
OL,5,Cafter fire
OL,7,FLooking ahead, he said the tragedy
OL,8,Fcould present an opportunity to
OL,9,Frebuild improved facilities tailored
OL,10,Fto pupils' needs, adding that
OL,11,Fyesterday's government announcement on
OL,12,FSEND provision was "long overdue".
OL,14,FDevon and Cornwall Police said the
OL,15,Fcause of the fire is not thought to be
OL,16,Fsuspicious.
OL,26,@tD@TOUtD@aO]
